{"tid":616084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最詭異「一桿進洞」　男與高爾夫球洞做愛","createTime":"2018-04-04T01:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-04T06:16:34.000Z","uid":122,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ac4af398247ffa0fffe8919c72c919f89ee33f88","tid":616084,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:26:59.000Z","msg":"英國貝賓頓(Bebington)的一處高爾夫球場，有一名男子的行為舉止相當詭異，竟然當場脫去上半身衣物，褲子也脫了一半，更與高爾夫球洞做愛，形成詭異的「一趕進洞」。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，當天去打高爾夫球的男子蓋頓(Steven Gayton)看到全程，並用手機拍攝下來。蓋頓表示，男子在現場對高爾夫球洞做出猥褻動作，相信他把陰莖放入高爾夫球洞，企圖洩慾射精，更疑似把旗桿拿來「開發」後庭小菊花。蓋頓也說：「我不認為這名男子是喝醉狀態，而且他還自拍，當時在球場上，除了我，還有其他3名友人。」他也表示，相信男子是一人來到高爾夫球場，也發現了蓋頓等人在拍攝與觀看，但男子似乎沒有太多抱怨或遮掩。<br />\n<br />\n男子完事後起身，穿上褲子後離開，蓋頓就說：「這應該是我這輩子最難忘的『高爾夫球賽』。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.bleacherreport.net/images_root/article/media_slots/photos/000/824/219/vanpersiegoal_original.gif?1366666927\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.bleacherreport.net%2Fimages_root%2Farticle%2Fmedia_slots%2Fphotos%2F000%2F824%2F219%2Fvanpersiegoal_original.gif%3F1366666927&h=4aaea0ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa9121344aaf808702cfe72d2f6a51a855d6f60e","tid":616084,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:31:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa8c75b0a99fe101e0b8790766648c99af53ce11","tid":616084,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9121344aaf808702cfe72d2f6a51a855d6f60e","tid":616084,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:31:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:57:35.000Z","msg":"台灣 = 正體蟲國"},{"pid":"f71658b089bfb2bb007bbf12d9585556fae912ba","tid":616084,"uid":26429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T01:58:12.000Z","msg":"施旖婕世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla